"Change Set:		7695ToolBuilder-Morphic-ar.35ToolBuilder-Morphic-ar.35:Implement font-chooser interface for Morphic."!!MorphicUIManager methodsFor: 'ui requests' stamp: 'ar 8/30/2009 17:01'!chooseFont: titleString for: aModel setSelector: setSelector getSelector: getSelector	"Open a font-chooser for the given model"	^FontChooserTool default		openWithWindowTitle: titleString 		for: aModel 		setSelector: setSelector 		getSelector: getSelector! !